{"tid":2178601,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Channel手足被捕？我一早就話XXXXXXX架啦！","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T11:14:18.000Z","uid":307619,"like":74,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14ada78c0ecb2d22b3ab8dccfb46097826888e15","tid":2178601,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:12:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">其實點解每次有手足出事<br />\n總係有啲人要衝出嚟話：<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>「一早就話乜乜乜...」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n下圖為例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yHN8Pn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yHN8Pn.png&h=bcb36911&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2smjfvT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2smjfvT.png&h=ef0fbc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明白出發點係好<br />\n冇人會想手足出事<br />\n<br />\n就好似個阿媽拖住個小朋友<br />\n個小朋友見到自己好鍾意嘅嘢所以跑<br />\n阿媽話佢再跑就會仆親<br />\n到個小朋友真係仆親嘅時候<br />\n<span class=\"red\">個阿媽係隔離話佢：「一早就叫咗你唔好跑㗎啦，而家咪仆親囉。」<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvrOTi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvrOTi0.png&h=89c29333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當下次有呢個諗法嘅時候<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"x-large\">不如試著說：「欣賞手足們嘅付出，但下次不如試吓XXXX方法，做多一重保障？」</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4b8d7dde8131004a5099efc08dcb22b9efeedd51","tid":2178601,"uid":233530,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:13:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔睬你都傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ebda2f578c367fdd23a1f0badfbb6a608dd918","tid":2178601,"uid":307619,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4b8d7dde8131004a5099efc08dcb22b9efeedd51","tid":2178601,"uid":233530,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:13:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔睬你都傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:13:55.